"otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[702,640],"id":"bf3b906e-46cf-427a-aac2-7c7611c47586","name":"Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"operation":"append","documentId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"list","value":"","cachedResultName":"Payload Tracker"},"sheetName":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"Main","cachedResultName":"Main"},"columns":{"mappingMode":"autoMapInputData","value":{},"matchingColumns":[],"schema":[]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.googleSheets","typeVersion":4.7,"position":[1026,1150],"id":"9d5378c7-2c9d-4a7a-bf67-dbef5605b5ba","name":"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"mode":"append","numberInputs":3},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.merge","typeVersion":3.2,"position":[1674,400],"id":"b5d25d4f-becc-41a6-a14e-d245b33484a9","name":"Merge Routed Work"},{"parameters":{"operation":"getCurrentDate","outputFieldName":"processedAt","options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.dateTime","typeVersion":2,"position":[2646,400],"id":"8a2c6fdc-0b48-4938-a0bc-17751a8aea3a","name":"Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"sortFieldsUi":{"sortField":[{"fieldName":"receivedAt","order":"descending"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.sort","typeVersion":1,"position":[2970,400],"id":"9d180e2d-1246-4b5a-880d-3a6050e04891","name":"Sort Payloads Newest First"},{"parameters":{"assignments":{"assignments":[{"id":"9e64101c-5050-4bef-b174-19e9ee4c1b19","name":"pipeline","value":"Data Transforms","type":"string"},{"id":"fc5d8e6e-e4c7-478a-a88e-ad0ead68dbcf","name":"version","value":"2.0","type":"string"}]},"options":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.set","typeVersion":3.4,"position":[3294,400],"id":"664e9efc-4a05-42e6-8338-f70b9ada02bb","name":"Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"select":"channel","channelId":{"__rl":true,"mode":"name","value":"#ops","cachedResultName":"#ops"},"text":"=✅ Ingest API callbacks with Google Sheets for your team — run completed at {{ $now.toFormat('HH:mm') }}","otherOptions":{}},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.slack","typeVersion":2.3,"position":[3618,400],"id":"5a70e655-81cf-4c12-8870-60a7220da30b","name":"Send Summary to Slack","retryOnFail":true,"maxTries":3,"waitBetweenTries":2000},{"parameters":{"content":"### Receive Inbound Webhook\n\nEntry point: listens for POST calls on `/wf09283-payload`. Use the TEST url while building, switch callers to the PRODUCTION url after publishing.\n\nNext: Route by Work Type","width":280,"height":232,"color":5},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-330,520],"id":"3ab9c119-29a8-7682-20a3-6d354a906a13","name":"Note: Receive Inbound Webhook"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Route by Work Type\n\nRoutes each item to one of 3 lanes: standard, priority + fallback.\n\nPorts: ①→ Process 'standard' → Google Sheets · ②→ Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert · ③→ Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-6,520],"id":"8ff90a85-5dc9-1ec1-86eb-c299ec5be9a6","name":"Note: Route by Work Type"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Process 'standard' → Google Sheets\n\ngoogleSheets — `appendOrUpdate` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Merge Routed Work\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[318,250],"id":"16a52291-0995-b679-b1ec-ba424f3fdb82","name":"Note: Process 'standard' → Google Sheets"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Merge Routed Work\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[642,760],"id":"c0b5a114-985c-9528-31c6-4af619c75466","name":"Note: Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)\n\ngoogleSheets — `append` operation against the connected account.\n\nNext: Merge Routed Work\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Google OAuth2 / service account","width":280,"height":232,"color":2},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[966,1270],"id":"0f979666-32b0-b5c3-eb53-9228708fe164","name":"Note: Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Merge Routed Work\n\nRejoins 3 branches into one stream (mode: append) so downstream logic runs once.\n\nNext: Stamp Processing Time","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[1614,520],"id":"11eedfa9-611b-9293-8ff1-cae155e2e1a2","name":"Note: Merge Routed Work"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Stamp Processing Time\n\nStamps `processedAt` with the current time for auditing.\n\nNext: Sort Payloads Newest First","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2586,520],"id":"f5dbe7b3-62bd-2bda-bda6-ecf5e8f61883","name":"Note: Stamp Processing Time"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Sort Payloads Newest First\n\nOrders items (newest first) so limits and digests pick the most relevant records.\n\nNext: Tag Pipeline Metadata","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[2910,520],"id":"96b5a052-7582-0bb7-7c91-02bc77c431ae","name":"Note: Sort Payloads Newest First"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Tag Pipeline Metadata\n\nShapes the item: writes `pipeline`, `version`. Keeps the schema explicit between stages.\n\nNext: Send Summary to Slack","width":280,"height":232,"color":7},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3234,520],"id":"69e53a12-467f-7c74-805a-e41222ab66aa","name":"Note: Tag Pipeline Metadata"},{"parameters":{"content":"### Send Summary to Slack\n\nslack — `action` operation against the connected account.\n\n↻ retries 3×/2s · 🔑 Slack OAuth2","width":280,"height":232,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[3558,520],"id":"a967c664-f423-1aad-6a52-c81126c170d8","name":"Note: Send Summary to Slack"},{"parameters":{"content":"# Ingest API callbacks with Google Sheets for your team\n\n**Pattern:** Webhook Pipeline · **Level:** Foundation · **Trigger:** Webhook\n\n## What it does\nIngest API callbacks with Google Sheets for your team. It fires the moment an external system calls its webhook.\n\n## Why it exists\nManual data transforms is slow and error-prone; this workflow makes the process repeatable, monitored and hands-off, with failures surfaced instead of silently lost.\n\n## Main flow\nReceive Inbound Webhook → Route by Work Type → Process 'standard' → Google Sheets → Merge Routed Work → Stamp Processing Time → Sort Payloads Newest First → Tag Pipeline Metadata → …\n\n## Use it for\n- Teams that want to webhook pipeline without manual effort\n- Anyone automating data transforms in software development\n- Replacing a fragile manual process with a reliable workflow\n\n## You get\n- Saves hours of manual work each week\n- Removes copy-paste errors\n- Has retries and error handling built in\n\n## Before first run\nConnect credentials: Google OAuth2 / service account; Slack OAuth2.\nFollow the color key: 🟦 entry · 🟪 AI · 🟫 actions · ⬜ utilities · 🟩 outputs · 🟥 error rail.\nEach node has its own doc card underneath — read those before editing.","width":480,"height":900},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-830,80],"id":"ae4a14aa-6324-2379-826d-0ef4a4e180b8","name":"📘 Workflow Overview"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🔐 Security\n\nNever trust inbound payloads: the webhook path is unguessable. Add header auth or IP allow-listing for defense in depth. Secrets live in n8n credentials — never in node parameters.","width":360,"height":260,"color":1},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[-230,-290],"id":"f28aa114-a2d9-78ca-651f-3235f76aad3a","name":"🔐 Security"},{"parameters":{"content":"## 🛠 Customize me\n\nQuick wins: point the data nodes at your own accounts (see 🔑 lines on each card), adjust the trigger cadence, and tune thresholds/labels to your data transforms process. Every node card explains its role — safe to extend at any marked branch.","width":360,"height":260,"color":4},"type":"n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote","typeVersion":1,"position":[190,-290],"id":"0c907bdc-b30d-5d43-12a2-68f0bd2763a4","name":"🛠 Customize me"}],"connections":{"Receive Inbound Webhook":{"main":[[{"node":"Route by Work Type","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Route by Work Type":{"main":[[{"node":"Process 'standard' → Google Sheets","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert","type":"main","index":0}],[{"node":"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Process 'standard' → Google Sheets":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Fast-Track 'priority' + Alert":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":1}]]},"Hold Unknown Types (DLQ)":{"main":[[{"node":"Merge Routed Work","type":"main","index":2}]]},"Merge Routed Work":{"main":[[{"node":"Stamp Processing Time","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Stamp Processing Time":{"main":[[{"node":"Sort Payloads Newest First","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Sort Payloads Newest First":{"main":[[{"node":"Tag Pipeline Metadata","type":"main","index":0}]]},"Tag Pipeline Metadata":{"main":[[{"node":"Send Summary to Slack","type":"main","index":0}]]}},"active":false,"settings":{"executionOrder":"v1"},"meta":{"templateCredsSetupCompleted":false},"tags":[],"pinData":{},"versionId":"9642811d-9006-4b08-8762-384702720fd8","id":"FDX09283"}